prvtHqosMIB.name: prvtHqosMIB
prvtHqosMIB.contactinfo: BATM/Telco Systems Support team Email: For North America: techsupport@telco.com For North Europe: support@batm.de, info@batm.de For the rest of the world: techsupport@telco.com
prvtHqosMIB.description: The private MIB module to manage Hierarchical Quality of Service.

PrvtHqosNamedItemOrNone.name: PrvtHqosNamedItemOrNone
PrvtHqosNamedItemOrNone.description: Same as PrvtHqosNamedItem except that a zero-length string is used to represent that no value is assigned.

PrvtHqosDot1pPriority.name: PrvtHqosDot1pPriority
PrvtHqosDot1pPriority.description: IEEE 802.1p priority. Zero is lowest, seven is highest.

PrvtHqosFcType.name: PrvtHqosFcType
PrvtHqosFcType.description: The name of a Forwarding Class.

PrvtHqosDscpValue.name: PrvtHqosDscpValue
PrvtHqosDscpValue.description: The value of a Differential Services Code Point.

PrvtHqosServiceQueueId.name: PrvtHqosServiceQueueId
PrvtHqosServiceQueueId.description: The identification number of a service queue.

PrvtHqosNetQueueIdType.name: PrvtHqosNetQueueIdType
PrvtHqosNetQueueIdType.description: The identification number of a network queue.

PrvtHqosServicePolicyId.name: PrvtHqosServicePolicyId
PrvtHqosServicePolicyId.description: The identification number of a service policy.

PrvtHqosNetPolNameType.name: PrvtHqosNetPolNameType
PrvtHqosNetPolNameType.description: The identification string of a network policy.

PrvtHqosNetPolNameOrNoneType.name: PrvtHqosNetPolNameOrNoneType
PrvtHqosNetPolNameOrNoneType.description: Same as PrvtHqosNetPolNameType except that a zero length string is used to represent no network policy.

PrvtHqosLevel.name: PrvtHqosLevel
PrvtHqosLevel.description: The priority level to apply to a packet.

PrvtHqosWeight.name: PrvtHqosWeight
PrvtHqosWeight.description: The weight of the specified entity while feeding into the parent.

PrvtHqosColorType.name: PrvtHqosColorType
PrvtHqosColorType.description: The traffic conformance level (i.e. traffic color).

PrvtHqosIfShaperId.name: PrvtHqosIfShaperId
PrvtHqosIfShaperId.description: The identifier of an Interface Shaper Profile.

PrvtHqosIfShaperIdOrNone.name: PrvtHqosIfShaperIdOrNone
PrvtHqosIfShaperIdOrNone.description: Same as PrvtHqosIfShaperId except that the value of zero represents no shaper profile.

PrvtHqosL1ShaperId.name: PrvtHqosL1ShaperId
PrvtHqosL1ShaperId.description: The identifier of a L1 Scheduler Shaper Profile.

PrvtHqosNetShaperId.name: PrvtHqosNetShaperId
PrvtHqosNetShaperId.description: The identifier of a Network Shaper Profile.

PrvtHqosL2ShaperId.name: PrvtHqosL2ShaperId
PrvtHqosL2ShaperId.description: The identifier of a L2 Scheduler Shaper Profile.

PrvtHqosPolicerIdType.name: PrvtHqosPolicerIdType
PrvtHqosPolicerIdType.description: The identifier of a Policer Profile.

PrvtHqosServWfqIdType.name: PrvtHqosServWfqIdType
PrvtHqosServWfqIdType.description: The identifier of a Service WFQ Profile.

PrvtHqosServSchedWfqIdType.name: PrvtHqosServSchedWfqIdType
PrvtHqosServSchedWfqIdType.description: The identifier of a Service Scheduler WFQ Profile.

PrvtHqosNetWfqIdType.name: PrvtHqosNetWfqIdType
PrvtHqosNetWfqIdType.description: The identifier of a Network WFQ Profile.

PrvtHqosWredIdType.name: PrvtHqosWredIdType
PrvtHqosWredIdType.description: The identifier of a WRED Profile.

PrvtHqosMapType.name: PrvtHqosMapType
PrvtHqosMapType.description: The type of mapping - VPT or DSCP.

PrvtHqosStatsCountType.name: PrvtHqosStatsCountType
PrvtHqosStatsCountType.description: The value of a statistics counter. The value is represented as an ASCII string.

prvtHqosSvcIngTable.name: prvtHqosSvcIngTable
prvtHqosSvcIngTable.description: Service Ingress Policy Table Each entry in this table defines a service ingress policy. Note that deletion of a row in this table will also result in the deletion of the dependent rows in the following tables: - prvtHqosSvcIngQueueTable - prvtHqosSvcIngFcTable - prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpTable - prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pTable - prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultTable - prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueTable

prvtHqosSvcIngId.name: prvtHqosSvcIngId
prvtHqosSvcIngId.description: Uniquely identifies a service ingress policy.

prvtHqosSvcIngRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcIngRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcIngRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this service ingress policy.

prvtHqosSvcIngDescr.name: prvtHqosSvcIngDescr
prvtHqosSvcIngDescr.description: User-defined description for the service ingress policy.

prvtHqosSvcIngQueueTable.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQueueTable
prvtHqosSvcIngQueueTable.description: Service Ingress Policy Queue Table Entries in this table define queues belonging to service ingress policies. A queue is specified using a unique queue identifier (prvtHqosSvcIngQueueId), and its parent scheduler policy name (prvtHqosSchedIngPolicyName) and scheduler name (prvtHqosSchedIngVirtName).

prvtHqosSvcIngQueueId.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQueueId
prvtHqosSvcIngQueueId.description: Uniquely identifies a queue belonging to a service ingress policy.

prvtHqosSvcIngQueueRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQueueRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcIngQueueRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this service ingress policy queue.

prvtHqosSvcIngQueueServWfq.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQueueServWfq
prvtHqosSvcIngQueueServWfq.description: The WFQ profile that needs to be used by the scheduler to which the queue would be feeding to. Must be set to the prvtHqosWfqSvcIngPrfId of an entry existing in prvtHqosWfqSvcIngPrfTable.

prvtHqosSvcIngQueueWred.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQueueWred
prvtHqosSvcIngQueueWred.description: The WRED profile applied to this service ingress policy queue. Must be set to the prvtHqosWredPrfId of an entry existing in prvtHqosWredPrfTable.

prvtHqosSvcIngQueuePolicer.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQueuePolicer
prvtHqosSvcIngQueuePolicer.description: The policer profile applied to this service ingress policy queue. Must be set to the prvtHqosPolicerSvcPrfId of an entry existing in prvtHqosPolicerSvcPrfTable.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcTable.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcTable
prvtHqosSvcIngFcTable.description: Service Ingress Policy FC Table A list of forwarding classes belonging to service ingress policies. Note that deletion of a row in this table will also result in the deletion of the dependent rows in the following tables: - prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpTable - prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pTable - prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultTable - prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueTable

prvtHqosSvcIngFcType.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcType
prvtHqosSvcIngFcType.description: The forwarding class to which this row applies.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcIngFcRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this forwarding class.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpTable.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpTable
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpTable.description: Service Ingress Policy FC DSCP Mapping Table Each entry in this table defines a DSCP to forwarding class mapping. Note that DSCP to FC mappings can not be used together with Dot1p (VPT) to FC mappings.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpValue.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpValue
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpValue.description: The Differentiated Services Code Point value to match in the packet.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this DSCP value.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpColor.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpColor
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDscpColor.description: The color (conformance level) to apply to traffic matching this row's DSCP value.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pTable.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pTable
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pTable.description: Service Ingress Policy FC Dot1p Mapping Table Each entry in this table defines a Dot1p (VPT) to forwarding class mapping. Note that VPT to FC mappings can not be used together with DSCP to FC mappings.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pValue.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pValue
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pValue.description: The Dot1p (VPT) value to match in the packet.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this service ingress policy's Dot1p entry.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pColor.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pColor
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDot1pColor.description: The color (conformance level) to apply to traffic matching this forwarding-class's Dot1p value.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultTable.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultTable
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultTable.description: Service Ingress Policy FC Default Mapping Table This table is used to configure, for each forwarding class, the default settings for all VPT or DSCP values. Only one entry may be created for each service policy's forwarding class (i.e. per prvtHqosSvcIngId, prvtHqosSvcIngFcType combination).

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultMapType.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultMapType
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultMapType.description: The mapping type (DSCP, or VPT) to which this row applies.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this mapping type.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultColor.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultColor
prvtHqosSvcIngFcDefaultColor.description: The default color (conformance level) to apply for all values (DSCP/VPT) applicable for the mapping type.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueTable.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueTable
prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueTable.description: Service Ingress Policy FC Queue Table This table maintains, for service ingress policies, the mapping of a particular forwarding class traffic type into a specified queue. A queue is specified using a unique queue identifier (prvtHqosSvcIngQueueId), and its parent scheduler policy name (prvtHqosSchedIngPolicyName) and scheduler name (prvtHqosSchedIngVirtName).

prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueType.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueType
prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueType.description: The type (unicast/multicast/broadcast) of the queue to which this row applies.

prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcIngFcQueueRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this forwarding class queue.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsTable.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsTable
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsTable.description: Service Ingress Queue Statistics Table Entries in this table contain the per-port statistics for service ingress queues.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsGrnBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsGrnBytes
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsGrnBytes.description: The total number of bytes of green traffic.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsGrnPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsGrnPckts
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsGrnPckts.description: The total number of packets of green traffic.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsYlwBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsYlwBytes
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsYlwBytes.description: The total number of bytes of yellow traffic.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsYlwPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsYlwPckts
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsYlwPckts.description: The total number of packets of yellow traffic.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsTxBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsTxBytes
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsTxBytes.description: The total number of bytes of traffic transmitted.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsTxPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsTxPckts
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsTxPckts.description: The total number of packets of traffic transmitted.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredGrnBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredGrnBytes
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredGrnBytes.description: The total number of bytes of green traffic dropped due to the WRED.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredGrnPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredGrnPckts
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredGrnPckts.description: The total number of packets of green traffic dropped due to the WRED.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredYlwBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredYlwBytes
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredYlwBytes.description: The total number of bytes of yellow traffic dropped due to the WRED.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredYlwPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredYlwPckts
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsWredYlwPckts.description: The total number of packets of yellow traffic dropped due to the WRED.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsPolDropBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsPolDropBytes
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsPolDropBytes.description: The total number of bytes of traffic dropped due to the policer.

prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsPolDropPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsPolDropPckts
prvtHqosSvcIngQStatsPolDropPckts.description: The total number of packets of traffic dropped due to the policer.

prvtHqosSvcEgrTable.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrTable
prvtHqosSvcEgrTable.description: Service Egress Policy Table Each entry in this table defines a service egress policy. Note that deletion of a row in this table will also result in the deletion of the dependent rows in the following tables: - prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueTable - prvtHqosSvcEgrFcTable - prvtHqosSvcEgrFcQueueTable

prvtHqosSvcEgrId.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrId
prvtHqosSvcEgrId.description: Uniquely identifies a service egress policy.

prvtHqosSvcEgrRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcEgrRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this service egress policy.

prvtHqosSvcEgrDescr.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrDescr
prvtHqosSvcEgrDescr.description: User-defined description for the service egress policy.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueTable.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueTable
prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueTable.description: Service Egress Policy Queue Table Entries in this table define queues belonging to service egress policies. A queue is specified using a unique queue identifier (prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueId), and its parent scheduler policy name (prvtHqosSchedEgrPolicyName) and scheduler name (prvtHqosSchedEgrVirtName).

prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueId.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueId
prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueId.description: Uniquely identifies a queue belonging to a service egress policy.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this service egress policy queue.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueServWfq.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueServWfq
prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueServWfq.description: The WFQ profile that needs to be used by the scheduler to which the queue would be feeding to. Must be set to the prvtHqosWfqSvcEgrPrfId of an entry existing in prvtHqosWfqSvcEgrPrfTable.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueWred.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueWred
prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueWred.description: The WRED profile applied to this service egress policy queue. Must be set to the prvtHqosWredPrfId of an entry existing in prvtHqosWredPrfTable.

prvtHqosSvcEgrFcTable.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrFcTable
prvtHqosSvcEgrFcTable.description: Service Egress Policy FC Mapping Table This table allows configuration that is specific to a forwarding class. Before a row for a specific forwarding class may be created in prvtHqosSvcEgrFcQueueTable, or in prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorTable, a row with that forwarding class must first be created in this table. Note that deletion of a row in this table will also result in the deletion of the dependent rows in prvtHqosSvcEgrFcQueueTable, and prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorTable.

prvtHqosSvcEgrFcNumber.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrFcNumber
prvtHqosSvcEgrFcNumber.description: The forwarding class to which this row applies.

prvtHqosSvcEgrFcRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrFcRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcEgrFcRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this forwarding class.

prvtHqosSvcEgrFcQueueTable.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrFcQueueTable
prvtHqosSvcEgrFcQueueTable.description: Service Egress Policy FC Queue Table This table maintains, for service egress policies, the mapping of traffic forwarding class into a specified queue. A queue is specified using a unique queue identifier (prvtHqosSvcEgrQueueId), and its parent scheduler policy name (prvtHqosSchedEgrPolicyName) and scheduler name (prvtHqosSchedEgrVirtName).

prvtHqosSvcEgrFcQueueType.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrFcQueueType
prvtHqosSvcEgrFcQueueType.description: The type (unicast/multicast/broadcast) of the queue to which this row applies.

prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorTable.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorTable
prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorTable.description: Service Egress Policy FC Color Table This table allows remarking of VPT bits based on forwarding class and color.

prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorValue.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorValue
prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorValue.description: The traffic color (conformance level) to which this row applies.

prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorRowStatus.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorRowStatus
prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this forwarding class and color.

prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorDot1PValue.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorDot1PValue
prvtHqosSvcEgrFcColorDot1PValue.description: The 802.1p value to use for packet remarking for traffic belonging to this forwarding class and color.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsTable.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsTable
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsTable.description: Service Egress Queue Statistics Table Entries in this table contain the per-port statistics for service egress queues.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsGrnBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsGrnBytes
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsGrnBytes.description: The total number of bytes of green traffic.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsGrnPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsGrnPckts
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsGrnPckts.description: The total number of packets of green traffic.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsYlwBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsYlwBytes
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsYlwBytes.description: The total number of bytes of yellow traffic.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsYlwPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsYlwPckts
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsYlwPckts.description: The total number of packets of yellow traffic.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsTxBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsTxBytes
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsTxBytes.description: The total number of bytes of traffic transmitted.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsTxPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsTxPckts
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsTxPckts.description: The total number of packets of traffic transmitted.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredGrnBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredGrnBytes
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredGrnBytes.description: The total number of bytes of green traffic dropped due to the WRED.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredGrnPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredGrnPckts
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredGrnPckts.description: The total number of packets of green traffic dropped due to the WRED.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredYlwBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredYlwBytes
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredYlwBytes.description: The total number of bytes of yellow traffic dropped due to the WRED.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredYlwPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredYlwPckts
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsWredYlwPckts.description: The total number of packets of yellow traffic dropped due to the WRED.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsPolDropBytes.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsPolDropBytes
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsPolDropBytes.description: The total number of bytes of traffic dropped due to the policer.

prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsPolDropPckts.name: prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsPolDropPckts
prvtHqosSvcEgrQStatsPolDropPckts.description: The total number of packets of traffic dropped due to the policer.

prvtHqosNetPolicyTable.name: prvtHqosNetPolicyTable
prvtHqosNetPolicyTable.description: Network Policy Table Each entry in this table defines a network (ingress or egress) policy. Note that deletion of a row in this table will also result in the deletion of the dependent rows in the following tables: - prvtHqosNetIngLspExpTable - prvtHqosNetEgrFcTable

prvtHqosNetPolicyRowStatus.name: prvtHqosNetPolicyRowStatus
prvtHqosNetPolicyRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this network policy.

prvtHqosNetPolicyDescr.name: prvtHqosNetPolicyDescr
prvtHqosNetPolicyDescr.description: User-defined description for the network policy

prvtHqosNetIngLspExpTable.name: prvtHqosNetIngLspExpTable
prvtHqosNetIngLspExpTable.description: Network Ingress Policy LSP EXP Mapping Table This table contains network ingress policies' LSP EXP bits to forwarding class and color mappings.

prvtHqosNetIngLspExpValue.name: prvtHqosNetIngLspExpValue
prvtHqosNetIngLspExpValue.description: The LSP EXP bit value to which this row applies.

prvtHqosNetIngLspExpRowStatus.name: prvtHqosNetIngLspExpRowStatus
prvtHqosNetIngLspExpRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this LSP EXP bit value.

prvtHqosNetIngLspExpFC.name: prvtHqosNetIngLspExpFC
prvtHqosNetIngLspExpFC.description: The forwarding class to assign to traffic matching the LSP EXP bit value.

prvtHqosNetIngLspExpColor.name: prvtHqosNetIngLspExpColor
prvtHqosNetIngLspExpColor.description: The color (conformance level) to assign to traffic matching the LSP EXP bit value.

prvtHqosNetEgrFcTable.name: prvtHqosNetEgrFcTable
prvtHqosNetEgrFcTable.description: Network Egress FC Mapping Table This table allows remarking of LSP EXP bits based on forwarding class and color.

prvtHqosNetEgrFcNumber.name: prvtHqosNetEgrFcNumber
prvtHqosNetEgrFcNumber.description: The forwarding class to which this row applies.

prvtHqosNetEgrFcColor.name: prvtHqosNetEgrFcColor
prvtHqosNetEgrFcColor.description: The traffic color (conformance level) to which this row applies.

prvtHqosNetEgrFcRowStatus.name: prvtHqosNetEgrFcRowStatus
prvtHqosNetEgrFcRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this forwarding class and color.

prvtHqosNetEgrFcLspExpValue.name: prvtHqosNetEgrFcLspExpValue
prvtHqosNetEgrFcLspExpValue.description: The value to assign to the LSP EXP bits of traffic belonging to the forwarding class and color.

prvtHqosNetQPolicyTable.name: prvtHqosNetQPolicyTable
prvtHqosNetQPolicyTable.description: Network Egress Queue Policy Table Each entry in this table defines a network egress queue policy. Note that deletion of a row in this table will also result in the deletion of the dependent rows in the following tables: - prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueTable - prvtHqosNetQPolicyFcTable - prvtHqosNetQPolicyFcQueueTable

prvtHqosNetQPolicyName.name: prvtHqosNetQPolicyName
prvtHqosNetQPolicyName.description: Uniquely identifies a network egress queue policy.

prvtHqosNetQPolicyRowStatus.name: prvtHqosNetQPolicyRowStatus
prvtHqosNetQPolicyRowStatus.description: The RowStatus for this network egress queue policy.

prvtHqosNetQPolicyDescr.name: prvtHqosNetQPolicyDescr
prvtHqosNetQPolicyDescr.description: User-defined description for the network egress queue policy.

prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueTable.name: prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueTable
prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueTable.description: Network Egress Queue Table Entries in this table define queues belonging to network (egress) queue policies.

prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueId.name: prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueId
prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueId.description: Uniquely identifies a queue belonging to a network (egress) queue policy.

prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueLevel.name: prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueLevel
prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueLevel.description: Specifies the level of priority for the queue while feeding to the parent.

prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueWfq.name: prvtHqosNetQPolicyQueueWfq
